[
  {
    "key": "285db421dde6f5bb8b0df2eb451a601f6425d4083ee4ded41980c845a8d30c76",
    "original": "Along the road...",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Title = \"Along the road...\""
  },
  {
    "key": "bb2ded3c056f01ebc7784fd3c8c1a50714856facaf95351b1830485cef0e64d8",
    "original": "I look forward to killing you twice, then.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"I look forward to killing you twice, then.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "53621af14e6a48649a6da993f200edfe0f736fea77ba06c0b0d44b57251430e4",
    "original": "No good deed goes unpunished.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"No good deed goes unpunished.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "b368b2e0e49490679a5b894963d56e8773d4df3c57d36437cb4ba8ba2e5ab962",
    "original": "This isn't our problem.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"This isn't our problem.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "646b23214cbb2cb8b7d929e5133c0c9c89512c926d63d8db39eb6c8ee8a33478",
    "original": "We can spare a bit of food.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"We can spare a bit of food.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "077f22f79a698c86fad8ccac70b7d48afdd9bdfde4022afcbacd2b6b7948486a",
    "original": "We do what we can.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"We do what we can.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "206a22ae79743f3b9862628939132ec211d951f223ce6d2a7b925ba56a76f2d9",
    "original": "You lose ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"You lose \" + item.getName()"
  },
  {
    "key": "4c68991d2ca1c3495cb3f65080ee49b6710e0b6375c3d1181def88ab7c793701",
    "original": "You'll only make the undead ranks swell. Better we finish you now.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"You'll only make the undead ranks swell. Better we finish you now.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "dd7b045db53ad12fd8b37c646ec7f840ebd0b662efc6a8c6b74ff95f4b3d547b",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_29.png[/img]You tell %randombrother% to hand out some food and supplies. The elder thanks you and says he'll speak highly of the %companyname% wherever he goes. Taking a piece of bread, you squat beside a sickly child and the father holding him. But when you hold the loaf out, the child turns its head up and bites into his father's neck. Any peasant healthy enough to stand does so and runs off. The rest... well, the rest shamble to their feet, faces pale, jaws slacked, eyes glowing red with furious hunger. You quickly order the mercenaries into formation.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_29.png[/img]You tell %randombrother% to hand out some food and supplies. The elder thanks you and says he'll speak highly of the %companyname% wherever he goes. Taking a piece of bread, you squat beside a sickly child and the father holding him. But when you hold the loaf out, the child turns its head up and bites into his father's neck. Any peasant healthy enough to stand does so and runs off. The rest... well, the rest shamble to their feet, faces pale, jaws slacked, eyes glowing red with furious hunger. You quickly order the mercenaries into formation.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "7a8d5c00831fde3bd3e3b2dd29197f373891379d83f4fa481c3157fc1753f7a5",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_59.png[/img]You come across a group of peasants sitting by the edge of the path. Men, women, children. Dirtied clothes, muddied boots, sores on their skin. A few carry wounds shaped like bitemarks. The eldest of the party speaks.%SPEECH_ON%Please, sir, do you have any food or water to give us?%SPEECH_OFF%He seems to see you eyeing the pustules and bitemarks. He shakes his head.%SPEECH_ON%Oh, don't mind those. Simple fox huntin' gone awry. We could just use a bit of help and then we can be on our way.%SPEECH_OFF%",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_59.png[/img]You come across a group of peasants sitting by the edge of the path. Men, women, children. Dirtied clothes, muddied boots, sores on their skin. A few carry wounds shaped like bitemarks. The eldest of the party speaks.%SPEECH_ON%Please, sir, do you have any food or water to give us?%SPEECH_OFF%He seems to see you eyeing the pustules and bitemarks. He shakes his head.%SPEECH_ON%Oh, don't mind those. Simple fox huntin' gone awry. We could just use a bit of help and then we can be on our way.%SPEECH_OFF%\""
  },
  {
    "key": "99a8f41569920eaeb3ab32e7ae17b8b0d41622a81ba227936f22b2259a040f84",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_59.png[/img]You command these sickened souls to be well - by commanding your men to kill them all. The elder leads the women and children away while the men rise up to stand their ground. One, wavering on green and peeling legs, points at you.%SPEECH_ON%What a saint you are ya prick. I hope I do come back from the dead. I hope my corpse kills the lot of you ya farkin' savages.%SPEECH_OFF%",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_59.png[/img]You command these sickened souls to be well - by commanding your men to kill them all. The elder leads the women and children away while the men rise up to stand their ground. One, wavering on green and peeling legs, points at you.%SPEECH_ON%What a saint you are ya prick. I hope I do come back from the dead. I hope my corpse kills the lot of you ya farkin' savages.%SPEECH_OFF%\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e980502ac1e4d871e14051a8725d8c55550fb20fd1b68282da9d708650dba76d",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_59.png[/img]You tell %randombrother% to hand out some food and supplies. The elder thanks you and says he'll speak highly of the %companyname% wherever he goes. A few of the men seem relieved that you didn't ask something awful of them.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_59.png[/img]You tell %randombrother% to hand out some food and supplies. The elder thanks you and says he'll speak highly of the %companyname% wherever he goes. A few of the men seem relieved that you didn't ask something awful of them.\""
  }
]